PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. JOSEPH A. GHIZ, a Judge of the Trial Division of the Supreme Court of Prince Edward Island, who was required to relocate from the City of Halifax, Nova Scotia, to the City of Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island.
